Region.ОбработчикиСобытийФормы.Description=Expected parameters\:\nMainFormIdentifier              - UUID - identifier of the form whose storage is used\nfor exchange.\nCompositionSchemaAddress        - String - address of temporary storage of the composition schema\nwhose settings are edited.\nFilterComposerSettingsAddress   - String - address of temporary storage of the composer settings being edited.\nFilterAreaPresentation          - String - presentation used to build the header.\nReturned as the selection result\:\nUndefined - Edit cancelled.\nString    - Address of temporary storage of the new composer settings.
